00:21:02.027 --> 00:21:03.629 align:middle line:84%
You put a room full
of men together.

00:21:03.629 --> 00:21:06.832 align:middle line:84%
You have someone who is
maybe earning half a million,

00:21:06.832 --> 00:21:09.068 align:middle line:84%
