a year, someone

00:21:09.068 --> 00:21:11.170 align:middle line:84%
who owns their own
corporation, someone

00:21:11.170 --> 00:21:13.806 align:middle line:84%
else who is a heavyweight
in some sector.

00:21:13.806 --> 00:21:16.675 align:middle line:84%
And then you have someone
who maybe is struggling

00:21:16.675 --> 00:21:19.245 align:middle line:84%
to make ends meet,
and they're concerned

00:21:19.245 --> 00:21:21.747 align:middle line:84%
