job next year for their family.

00:21:21.747 --> 00:21:25.217 align:middle line:84%
And on and on and on, you go
around this room of individuals

00:21:25.217 --> 00:21:29.021 align:middle line:84%
with a diverse kinds of
economic portfolios, as it were.

00:21:29.021 --> 00:21:31.423 align:middle line:84%
You can tell exactly
how, in the way

00:21:31.423 --> 00:21:32.925 align:middle line:84%
our culture is
structured today, you

00:21:32.925 --> 00:21:35.227 align:middle line:84%
can tell exactly how
each of those persons

00:21:35.227 --> 00:21:36.328 align:middle line:90%
feels about themselves.

00:21:36.328 --> 00:21:37.329 align:middle line:90%
>>TELLINGER: Exactly.

00:21:37.329 --> 00:21:38.764 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And that
it's so directly

00:21:38.764 --> 00:21:42.101 align:middle line:84%
linked to money, the
self-esteem, the fear,

00:21:42.101 --> 00:21:43.869 align:middle line:90%
the sense of self-worth.

00:21:43.869 --> 00:21:45.004 align:middle line:90%
>>TELLINGER: And it's all--

00:21:45.004 --> 00:21:48.073 align:middle line:84%
Look, unfortunately,
this is the situation.

00:21:48.073 --> 00:21:49.241 align:middle line:90%
No matter how you argue it.

00:21:49.241 --> 00:21:52.044 align:middle line:84%
You can argue in favor
of money, that it's

00:21:52.044 --> 00:21:54.079 align:middle line:90%
an exchange of energy.

00:21:54.079 --> 00:21:54.947 align:middle line:90%
And it's not money.

00:21:54.947 --> 00:21:57.116 align:middle line:84%
It's the love of money
that causes the problems.

00:21:57.116 --> 00:21:59.251 align:middle line:84%
You know what, I've been
through this thousands

00:21:59.251 --> 00:22:00.219 align:middle line:90%
and thousands of times.

00:22:00.219 --> 00:22:02.721 align:middle line:90%
No, no, no, no on every level.

00:22:02.721 --> 00:22:04.990 align:middle line:90%
It is money that is the problem.

00:22:04.990 --> 00:22:07.459 align:middle line:84%
It's the money that
causes all the problems,

00:22:07.459 --> 00:22:11.263 align:middle line:84%
money that's responsible for
the gluttony and the greed

00:22:11.263 --> 00:22:14.266 align:middle line:84%
and the hoarding and the
ugliness and the seven

00:22:14.266 --> 00:22:15.267 align:middle line:90%
deadly sins.

00:22:15.267 --> 00:22:16.368 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Competition.

00:22:16.368 --> 00:22:17.403 align:middle line:90%
>>TELLINGER: Competition.

00:22:17.403 --> 00:22:19.171 align:middle line:84%
The hierarchial
structure system.

00:22:19.171 --> 00:22:21.540 align:middle line:90%
So let's get to the good news.

00:22:21.540 --> 00:22:24.944 align:middle line:84%
The good news is that you
can solve all these problems,

00:22:24.944 --> 00:22:27.746 align:middle line:84%
because we can harp
on the negative,

00:22:27.746 --> 00:22:30.583 align:middle line:84%
but let's provide your
viewers with a solution.

00:22:30.583 --> 00:22:32.418 align:middle line:84%
And the solution
is really simple.

00:22:32.418 --> 00:22:34.453 align:middle line:90%
Get rid of money.

00:22:34.453 --> 00:22:37.356 align:middle line:84%
As horrific as it may seem
for the next few seconds

00:22:37.356 --> 00:22:40.392 align:middle line:84%
or few minutes or few
weeks for some people--

00:22:40.392 --> 00:22:42.094 align:middle line:84%
Because some people
get it instantly.

00:22:42.094 --> 00:22:43.829 align:middle line:84%
Some people take a
little while to get it.

00:22:43.829 --> 00:22:45.531 align:middle line:84%
And some people really
struggle with it

00:22:45.531 --> 00:22:50.402 align:middle line:84%
because they really grounded in
the capitalistic, consumeristic

00:22:50.402 --> 00:22:53.072 align:middle line:84%
society that we've
become of me, me, me.

00:22:53.072 --> 00:22:53.906 align:middle line:90%
What's in it for me?

00:22:53.906 --> 00:22:55.608 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So we need
a make believe world

00:22:55.608 --> 00:22:57.543 align:middle line:84%
