verbally right now,

00:22:57.543 --> 00:22:59.111 align:middle line:90%
a world without money.

00:22:59.111 --> 00:23:02.081 align:middle line:84%
You can be safe because, for the
moment, it's just theoretical.

00:23:02.081 --> 00:23:03.515 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: It's
