00:23:03.515 --> 00:23:06.285 align:middle line:84%
But allow yourself to expand
your mind and think about this.

00:23:06.285 --> 00:23:10.189 align:middle line:84%
And remember that quantum
physics and the metaphysics

00:23:10.189 --> 00:23:12.758 align:middle line:84%
and the beautiful
beings of light

00:23:12.758 --> 00:23:15.694 align:middle line:84%
out there teaching us that
we can manifest things

00:23:15.694 --> 00:23:18.464 align:middle line:84%
with our mind, the laws of
attraction, all these things.

00:23:18.464 --> 00:23:23.235 align:middle line:84%
So if we project a beautiful
world of unity consciousness,

00:23:23.235 --> 00:23:26.872 align:middle line:84%
where everybody shares and
everybody contributes what

00:23:26.872 --> 00:23:30.242 align:middle line:84%
their passion is towards their
society and their community,

00:23:30.242 --> 00:23:34.179 align:middle line:84%
there'll be an abundance of
all for everyone at all times.

00:23:34.179 --> 00:23:37.416 align:middle line:84%
That is really the
utopian structure of this.

00:23:37.416 --> 00:23:39.451 align:middle line:84%
And I also just need to
just throw this in there,

00:23:39.451 --> 00:23:41.420 align:middle line:84%
because some people,
as we said earlier,

00:23:41.420 --> 00:23:43.822 align:middle line:84%
believe that money is the
consequence of barter and trade

00:23:43.822 --> 00:23:44.757 align:middle line:90%
and all that.

00:23:44.757 --> 00:23:45.724 align:middle line:90%
That's not the case.

00:23:45.724 --> 00:23:50.529 align:middle line:84%
And that is why the
contributionist Ubuntu system

00:23:50.529 --> 00:23:54.967 align:middle line:84%
has no barter, no trade, no
value attached to anything,

00:23:54.967 --> 00:23:59.038 align:middle line:84%
greater or lesser, because
in the Ubuntu communities

00:23:59.038 --> 00:24:01.140 align:middle line:90%
everyone is equally valued.

00:24:01.140 --> 00:24:02.675 align:middle line:84%
Your time and your
effort and energy,

00:24:02.675 --> 00:24:04.610 align:middle line:84%
what you do for
your community is

00:24:04.610 --> 00:24:06.879 align:middle line:90%
valued as much as anybody else.

00:24:06.879 --> 00:24:08.814 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And this is a
really important part.

00:24:08.814 --> 00:24:12.751 align:middle line:84%
Every person and with the skill
that they bring to the table

00:24:12.751 --> 00:24:16.922 align:middle line:84%
is an important part
of an entire system.

00:24:16.922 --> 00:24:20.359 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: So in a nutshell,
the definition of an Ubuntu

00:24:20.359 --> 00:24:23.729 align:middle line:84%
