How is that going to work?

00:24:36.575 --> 00:24:37.643 align:middle line:90%
How is that going to work?

00:24:37.643 --> 00:24:41.947 align:middle line:84%
Just repeat the mantra, the
five-pointed mantra, right,

00:24:41.947 --> 00:24:43.615 align:middle line:90%
the five-factor mantra.

00:24:43.615 --> 00:24:48.020 align:middle line:84%
--no money, no barter,
no trade, no value

00:24:48.020 --> 00:24:51.056 align:middle line:84%
attached to anything
