00:24:51.056 --> 00:24:54.560 align:middle line:84%
than anyone else's value,
where everybody contributes

00:24:54.560 --> 00:24:58.630 align:middle line:84%
their natural talents, God-given
skills, God-given talents

00:24:58.630 --> 00:25:00.766 align:middle line:84%
or acquired skills
for the greater

00:25:00.766 --> 00:25:03.369 align:middle line:84%
benefit of all in
their community.

00:25:03.369 --> 00:25:04.470 align:middle line:90%
Those are the five points.

