How would this start?

00:26:24.783 --> 00:26:26.819 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: Well, I
think every little town

00:26:26.819 --> 00:26:28.754 align:middle line:90%
can use this as a little model.

00:26:28.754 --> 00:26:31.190 align:middle line:84%
Whether it's a small
town or a small village,

00:26:31.190 --> 00:26:34.860 align:middle line:84%
