Once you don't have
to pay electricity

00:28:28.407 --> 00:28:30.342 align:middle line:84%
for the electricity
providing companies

00:28:30.342 --> 00:28:32.177 align:middle line:84%
and you supply
yourself with energy,

00:28:32.177 --> 00:28:36.148 align:middle line:84%
you've got enough milk,
bread, butter, cheese, eggs.

00:28:36.148 --> 00:28:38.717 align:middle line:84%
You've got gas coming
from the sewage plant.

