Suddenly you're looking at
a whole different community.

00:28:41.653 --> 00:28:43.221 align:middle line:90%
Suddenly there's more time.

00:28:43.221 --> 00:28:44.890 align:middle line:90%
Everyone's getting fed.

00:28:44.890 --> 00:28:49.094 align:middle line:84%
Everyone's got the
