of their day doing that,

00:37:24.909 --> 00:37:25.944 align:middle line:90%
it's just too much stuff.

00:37:25.944 --> 00:37:27.645 align:middle line:90%
So you've got to ease off.

00:37:27.645 --> 00:37:30.048 align:middle line:90%
Take the foot off the gas.

00:37:30.048 --> 00:37:30.882 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:37:30.882 --> 00:37:31.516 align:middle line:90%
Slow down.

00:37:31.516 --> 00:37:33.451 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, we're going
to have too much stuff.

00:37:33.451 --> 00:37:36.454 align:middle line:84%
And that applies on
every level of society

00:37:36.454 --> 00:37:39.324 align:middle line:84%
if you start to analyze what
we're talking about here.

00:37:39.324 --> 00:37:41.326 align:middle line:90%
What happens next?

00:37:41.326 --> 00:37:43.628 align:middle line:84%
Well, you're going to
finish what you love doing,

00:37:43.628 --> 00:37:45.897 align:middle line:84%
and then you've got
all this time left.

00:37:45.897 --> 00:37:48.266 align:middle line:84%
So you're going to do something
else that you love to do.

00:37:48.266 --> 00:37:50.835 align:middle line:84%
And that's the beauty
about our humanness.

00:37:50.835 --> 00:37:55.340 align:middle line:84%
We have many hobbies,
many loves, many passions.

00:37:55.340 --> 00:37:56.975 align:middle line:84%
And you can follow
another passion,

00:37:56.975 --> 00:38:00.278 align:middle line:84%
whether it's movie-making
or sculpturing.

00:38:00.278 --> 00:38:04.449 align:middle line:84%
And in this lies the
example of the other stuff.

00:38:04.449 --> 00:38:05.150 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:38:05.150 --> 00:38:08.219 align:middle line:84%
So now you go home, and you
start doing your sculptures.

00:38:08.219 --> 00:38:09.120 align:middle line:90%
But you're not doing--

00:38:09.120 --> 00:38:10.989 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Now, you have
secondary industries.

00:38:10.989 --> 00:38:13.458 align:middle line:84%
