of art starts coming in.

00:38:13.458 --> 00:38:16.227 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: But I'm using
this because often arts

00:38:16.227 --> 00:38:17.462 align:middle line:90%
is a questionable thing.

00:38:17.462 --> 00:38:20.565 align:middle line:84%
Well, why would the community
