00:38:20.565 --> 00:38:21.666 align:middle line:90%
and make statues?

00:38:21.666 --> 00:38:24.335 align:middle line:84%
You know, you're not
really benefiting anybody.

00:38:24.335 --> 00:38:25.937 align:middle line:90%
Well, I'll show you.

00:38:25.937 --> 00:38:28.806 align:middle line:84%
Again, once you work
through this process,

00:38:28.806 --> 00:38:30.608 align:middle line:90%
you will always get the answers.

