00:38:42.854 --> 00:38:45.490 align:middle line:84%
contributes their God-given
talents or their acquired

00:38:45.490 --> 00:38:48.760 align:middle line:84%
skills to the greater benefit
of all in their community.

00:38:48.760 --> 00:38:50.862 align:middle line:90%
The answers are so simple.

00:38:50.862 --> 00:38:53.865 align:middle line:90%
So just to quickly explain this.

00:38:53.865 --> 00:38:56.868 align:middle line:84%
So you finished your
working in the dairy,

00:38:56.868 --> 00:38:58.236 align:middle line:90%
because you love to make cheese.

00:38:58.236 --> 00:38:58.736 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:38:58.736 --> 00:39:02.040 align:middle line:84%
Now, you come home, or you
go to the communal area,

00:39:02.040 --> 00:39:04.642 align:middle line:84%
where you study under
the master sculptor.

00:39:04.642 --> 00:39:07.512 align:middle line:84%
And you start making
beautiful sculptures.

00:39:07.512 --> 00:39:10.882 align:middle line:84%
And within the six
months, there's

00:39:10.882 --> 00:39:13.351 align:middle line:84%
