00:39:24.295 --> 00:39:28.032 align:middle line:84%
And this is where we talk about
it's not a lawless society.

00:39:28.032 --> 00:39:32.136 align:middle line:84%
It's a very cohesively
structured society.

00:39:32.136 --> 00:39:35.139 align:middle line:84%
And it's based on what I
call the council of elders,

00:39:35.139 --> 00:39:37.609 align:middle line:84%
the 12 around 1, the
Christic principles,

00:39:37.609 --> 00:39:40.111 align:middle line:84%
the Christ consciousness
principles, the 12

00:39:40.111 --> 00:39:42.313 align:middle line:84%
disciples around
Christ, because that

00:39:42.313 --> 00:39:44.616 align:middle line:84%
is the perfect number
in sacred geometry

00:39:44.616 --> 00:39:49.320 align:middle line:84%
to have as your
decision-making council

00:39:49.320 --> 00:39:50.722 align:middle line:84%
And they're the
council of elders

00:39:50.722 --> 00:39:53.591 align:middle line:84%
that, on a daily basis
and an hourly basis,

00:39:53.591 --> 00:39:56.928 align:middle line:84%
decide what's best
for the community.

00:39:56.928 --> 00:39:58.129 align:middle line:90%
It is such a simple thing.

00:39:58.129 --> 00:40:01.466 align:middle line:84%
So a bunch of you will run
off to the council of elders

00:40:01.466 --> 00:40:04.969 align:middle line:84%
