for our town.

00:40:10.308 --> 00:40:12.377 align:middle line:84%
And the council of elders
will go, oh my goodness,

00:40:12.377 --> 00:40:12.610 align:middle line:90%
you're right.

00:40:12.610 --> 00:40:13.544 align:middle line:84%
Regina's sculptures
are everywhere.

00:40:13.544 --> 00:40:14.979 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: She's
done baking bread.

00:40:14.979 --> 00:40:17.148 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: Regina,
it's your choice.

00:40:17.148 --> 00:40:20.151 align:middle line:84%
Would you like to become the
officially appointed sculptor

00:40:20.151 --> 00:40:21.853 align:middle line:90%
for our town?

00:40:21.853 --> 00:40:23.388 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to
bake bread anymore.

00:40:23.388 --> 00:40:25.156 align:middle line:84%
And you'll say, well,
