00:40:25.156 --> 00:40:26.924 align:middle line:84%
but you know what, I
prefer making statues,

00:40:26.924 --> 00:40:28.626 align:middle line:84%
and if you'll allow
me to do that--

00:40:28.626 --> 00:40:30.461 align:middle line:84%
So what happens,
the community will

00:40:30.461 --> 00:40:34.165 align:middle line:84%
bestow the honor of doing what
it is you do for the community.

00:40:34.165 --> 00:40:36.834 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And what's interesting
about this is once the survival

00:40:36.834 --> 00:40:39.570 align:middle line:84%
needs are taken care
of, once the fear leaves

00:40:39.570 --> 00:40:41.906 align:middle line:84%
the cells of our body, which
most people don't know what

00:40:41.906 --> 00:40:46.077 align:middle line:84%
that feels like anymore
to truly be without fear,

00:40:46.077 --> 00:40:50.281 align:middle line:84%
and once that happens, our whole
psyche and internal landscape

00:40:50.281 --> 00:40:51.115 align:middle line:90%
shifts.

00:40:51.115 --> 00:40:54.552 align:middle line:84%
And beauty and
these other esoteric

00:40:54.552 --> 00:40:56.954 align:middle line:84%
and finer aspects
of life actually

00:40:56.954 --> 00:40:59.223 align:middle line:84%
start coming into
a place of not only

00:40:59.223 --> 00:41:01.292 align:middle line:84%
that we're able to
see them, but truly

00:41:01.292 --> 00:41:03.328 align:middle line:84%
being of a value
and appreciation.

00:41:03.328 --> 00:41:06.331 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: That's the
thing, the appreciation.

00:41:06.331 --> 00:41:10.001 align:middle line:84%
There is no better reward
