00:41:10.001 --> 00:41:12.870 align:middle line:84%
of others and the
recognition by others

00:41:12.870 --> 00:41:15.773 align:middle line:84%
for what it is that you are
doing for your community.

00:41:15.773 --> 00:41:18.643 align:middle line:84%
No amount of money
could ever even

00:41:18.643 --> 00:41:19.911 align:middle line:90%
begin to compare with that.

00:41:19.911 --> 00:41:22.613 align:middle line:84%
And this is, I believe, why
people have become incredibly

00:41:22.613 --> 00:41:25.516 align:middle line:84%
wealthy, and they realize
that money can't buy you love,

00:41:25.516 --> 00:41:29.087 align:middle line:84%
money can't buy you happiness,
they start giving it away.

00:41:29.087 --> 00:41:30.722 align:middle line:84%
Because once they
start giving it away,

00:41:30.722 --> 00:41:32.690 align:middle line:84%
they start to feel
the love of others

00:41:32.690 --> 00:41:36.527 align:middle line:84%
because it increases
the plight of others.

00:41:36.527 --> 00:41:40.031 align:middle line:84%
It helps them out of
areas of desperate needs.

00:41:40.031 --> 00:41:45.236 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly they start to feel
a different kind of energy,

00:41:45.236 --> 00:41:47.972 align:middle line:90%
and that changes people.

00:41:47.972 --> 00:41:49.574 align:middle line:84%
And within there is
an interesting mix.

00:41:49.574 --> 00:41:52.944 align:middle line:84%
And I think that, as we
move from the capitalistic

00:41:52.944 --> 00:41:56.080 align:middle line:84%
and the consumeristic societies
the ego-driven me, me,

00:41:56.080 --> 00:42:02.019 align:middle line:84%
me service to self, and changing
that into service to others--

00:42:02.019 --> 00:42:03.988 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Totally different
internal landscape.

00:42:03.988 --> 00:42:04.856 align:middle line:84%
>>TELLINGER: --people with
huge amounts of money,

00:42:04.856 --> 00:42:07.091 align:middle line:84%
I believe, will start
crawling out of the woodwork

00:42:07.091 --> 00:42:08.693 align:middle line:90%
and say, hold on.

00:42:08.693 --> 00:42:10.962 align:middle line:84%
That's what I'm going to
do with all this wealth

00:42:10.962 --> 00:42:12.029 align:middle line:90%
that I've acquired.

00:42:12.029 --> 00:42:14.999 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, what the hell
am I living this life for?

00:42:14.999 --> 00:42:17.101 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Even Darwin, in
his lesser known works,--

00:42:17.101 --> 00:42:19.971 align:middle line:84%
Everybody made a big deal out
of the competition and survival

00:42:19.971 --> 00:42:23.040 align:middle line:84%
of the fittest, which is really
only mentioned a few times.

00:42:23.040 --> 00:42:25.576 align:middle line:84%
--the greater part
of his work actually

00:42:25.576 --> 00:42:29.414 align:middle line:84%
was extolling the
virtues of cooperation.

00:42:29.414 --> 00:42:32.016 align:middle line:84%
Our survival is through
cooperation not competition.

00:42:32.016 --> 00:42:35.253 align:middle line:84%
And we have somehow
been convinced

00:42:35.253 --> 00:42:38.122 align:middle line:84%
that the other is true, keeping
us in this horrible state.

00:42:38.122 --> 00:42:39.824 align:middle line:84%
And that competition
doesn't happen just

00:42:39.824 --> 00:42:40.992 align:middle line:90%
between individuals.

00:42:40.992 --> 00:42:42.093 align:middle line:90%
It happens internally.

00:42:42.093 --> 00:42:44.462 align:middle line:84%
We're in internal
conflict ourselves.

00:42:44.462 --> 00:42:48.199 align:middle line:84%
And so what you're talking
about, imagining this world,

00:42:48.199 --> 00:42:50.635 align:middle line:84%
is where we're making
our contribution,

00:42:50.635 --> 00:42:52.270 align:middle line:84%
but someone else
is contributing.

00:42:52.270 --> 00:42:55.006 align:middle line:84%
It's coming up behind you
and flowing through you

00:42:55.006 --> 00:42:56.274 align:middle line:90%
in all directions.

00:42:56.274 --> 00:42:59.744 align:middle line:84%
There is nothing to fear
when you're all creating this

00:42:59.744 --> 00:43:00.478 align:middle line:90%
together.

00:43:00.478 --> 00:43:01.779 align:middle line:90%
>>TELLINGER: It's so beautiful.

00:43:01.779 --> 00:43:05.116 align:middle line:84%
Because what you did you touched
so many important nerve endings

00:43:05.116 --> 00:43:07.585 align:middle line:84%
and fundamentals
of contributionism.

00:43:07.585 --> 00:43:10.321 align:middle line:84%
First of all, the fact
that it's a united effort.

00:43:10.321 --> 00:43:11.989 align:middle line:90%
It's unity consciousness.

00:43:11.989 --> 00:43:14.425 align:middle line:84%
So I really believe
that it's only

00:43:14.425 --> 00:43:17.462 align:middle line:84%
through higher
consciousness levels

00:43:17.462 --> 00:43:19.430 align:middle line:84%
and as we grow into
the consciousness

00:43:19.430 --> 00:43:22.099 align:middle line:84%
that we start realizing that
that's the only way ahead.

00:43:22.099 --> 00:43:23.401 align:middle line:90%
It's the only way ahead.

00:43:23.401 --> 00:43:27.972 align:middle line:84%
It's a system for beings
of higher consciousness.

00:43:27.972 --> 00:43:32.710 align:middle line:84%
And secondly, the competition
thing is so absolutely crucial.

00:43:32.710 --> 00:43:33.811 align:middle line:90%
Competition, we talked.

00:43:33.811 --> 00:43:34.445 align:middle line:90%
Competition.

00:43:34.445 --> 00:43:35.913 align:middle line:90%
And it's no.

00:43:35.913 --> 00:43:37.782 align:middle line:90%
You want cooperation.

00:43:37.782 --> 00:43:40.251 align:middle line:84%
So there's another beautiful
example that I have for people

00:43:40.251 --> 00:43:42.587 align:middle line:90%
